lead_paragraph: Those who would be New York's representatives are hard at work making their final appeals to voters in a last push before Election Day.
snippet: Also in the Morning Buzz: A suspect is arrested in the killing of a bodega clerk, an art show hides in an abandoned subway station, and other regional news.
